== Festivals ==
=== Kamioka Festival ===
The collective term for the annual festivals of Ōtsu Shrine, {{ill|Hachiman Shrine (Hida City)|ja|八幡宮|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, and {{ill|Hakusan Shrine (Hida City)|ja|白山神社|qq=draft|qq=draft}}, celebrated on the same day. It is one of the "Three Great Festivals of Hida," alongside the {{ill|Takayama Festival|ja|高山祭|qq=draft|qq=draft}} and {{ill|Furukawa Festival|ja|古川祭|qq=draft|qq=draft}}.

=== Funatsu Bon Odori ===
Held annually from August 14 to 16 in the shrine precincts. It was designated as an intangible cultural property by [[Gifu Prefecture]] in 1969.<ref>{{Cite web|language=ja|date= |url=http://www.pref.gifu.lg.jp/kyoiku-bunka-sports/bunka-geijutsu/bunkazai-zuroku/bunkazai-zuroku/mumin/hidasi/funatubonn.html |title=Funatsu Bon Odori |publisher=Gifu Prefecture |accessdate=2012-10-16}}</ref>

