* {{ill|Takenu Nakawawake no Mikoto|ja|武渟河別命|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takenu Nakawawake no Mikoto|qq=}} - Son of Ōhiko no Mikoto.
* {{ill|Takeminakata|lt=Takeminakata no Mikoto|ja|建南方富命|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Takeminakata|qq=}} - Enshrined from {{ill|Suwa Shrine|ja|諏訪神社|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Suwa Shrine|qq=}}.

; Auxiliary Shrines
* Shinmei Shrine
''' {{ill|Amaterasu Ōmikami|ja|天照大神|1=Amaterasu|lt=Amaterasu Ōmikami|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Amaterasu Ōmikami|13=User:Immanuelle/Amaterasu|qq=}}
