* Kōzan Shrine
''' {{ill|Kanayamahiko no Kami|ja|金山彦大神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanayamahiko no Kami|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}
''' {{ill|Kanayamahime no Kami|ja|金山姫大神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kanayamahime no Kami|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}
* Sugawara Shrine
''' {{ill|Sugawara no Michizane|ja|Sugawara no Michizane|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sugawara no Michizane|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}
''' {{ill|Kotoshironushi-no-Mikoto|lt=Kotoshironushi-no-Mikoto|lt=Kotoshironushi|lt=Kotoshironushi no Kami|ja|事代主神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kotoshironushi|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 事代主}}
''' {{ill|Ebisu|ja|恵美須大神|qq=draft|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ebisu|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}}
